                    <div class="portfolio-box-caption">
                        <div class="project-category text-white-50">Gundam Model Kits</div>
                        <div class="project-name">Explore our extensive collection of Gundam model kits, featuring everything from classic Mobile Suits to the latest releases.</div>
                    </div>
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-6">
                <a class="portfolio-box" href="assets/image2.jpg" title="Tools and Accessories">
                    <img class="img-fluid" src="assets/image2.jpg" alt="..." />
                    <div class="portfolio-box-caption">
                        <div class="project-category text-white-50">Tools and Accessories</div>
                        <div class="project-name">Take your Gundam building experience to the next level with our premium selection of tools and accessories.</div>
