                        <div class="project-category text-white-50">Gift Sets and Starter Kits</div>
                        <div class="project-name">These sets come complete with everything you need to dive right into building, including essential tools, easy-to-follow instructions, and a carefully selected Gundam kit. </div>
                    </div>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
